Chain[a, {b1, b2, ...}, {c1, c2, ...}, d, ...] returns a list of links \
consecutively connecting a, bi, cj, d, ... for all i and j. Chain[a, {{b11, \
b12, ...}, {b21, b22, ...}}, c, ...] constructs a chain of links connecting \
